<h2 id='event-activity'>Event Activity</h2>
<p>The following functions provide Inspetor with information regarding the events (<em>e.g. parties, shows...</em>) listed on your platform:</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="#event-creation">trackEventCreation</a></li>
<li><a href="#event-updates">trackEventUpdate</a></li>
<li><a href="#event-deletion">trackEventDeletion</a></li>
</ul>

<p>All functions for tracking event activity require an <a href="#inspetorevent">InspetorEvent</a> object as argument and return <code>true</code> upon successful execution. Otherwise, one of the following exceptions will be thrown:</p>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Exception</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td><strong><a href="#inspetoreventexception">EventException</a></strong></td>
<td>The Event object provided is invalid</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong><a href="#inspetoraddressexception">AddressException</a></strong></td>
<td>The Address object provided as a property of the Event object is invalid</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong><a href="#inspetorgeneralexception">generalException</a></strong></td>
<td>The timestamps passed as Event object properties are invalid</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong><a href="#trackerexception">TrackerException</a></strong></td>
<td>An internal error occurred (<em>This should never happen</em>)</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

<p><h3 id='event-creation'>Event Creation</h3><pre class="highlight php tab-php"><code><span class="cp">&lt;?php</span>

<span class="k">use</span> <span class="nx">Inspetor</span><span class="p">;</span>

<span class="nv">$inspetor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nv">$this</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">getConfiguredInspetor</span><span class="p">();</span>

<span class="nv">$inspetor</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">trackEventCreation</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$event</span><span class="p">);</span>

<span class="cp">?&gt;</span>
</code></pre>
<p>Send information to Inspetor anytime a new event (<em>e.g. pary, shows...</em>) is created in your platform</p>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Argument</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>event</td>
<td>Inspetor/Model/<a href="#inspetorevent">InspetorEvent</a></td>
<td>The Event that is being created</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</p>

<p><h3 id='event-updates'>Event Updates</h3><pre class="highlight php tab-php"><code><span class="cp">&lt;?php</span>

<span class="k">use</span> <span class="nx">Inspetor</span><span class="p">;</span>

<span class="nv">$inspetor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nv">$this</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">getConfiguredInspetor</span><span class="p">();</span>

<span class="nv">$inspetor</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">trackEventUpdate</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$event</span><span class="p">);</span>

<span class="cp">?&gt;</span>
</code></pre>
<p>Send information to Inspetor every time an event listing&#39;s information is updated (event title, location, etc.)</p>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Argument</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>event</td>
<td>Inspetor/Model/<a href="#inspetorevent">InspetorEvent</a></td>
<td>The Event that is being updated</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</p>

<p><h3 id='event-deletion'>Event Deletion</h3><pre class="highlight php tab-php"><code><span class="cp">&lt;?php</span>

<span class="k">use</span> <span class="nx">Inspetor</span><span class="p">;</span>

<span class="nv">$inspetor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nv">$this</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">getConfiguredInspetor</span><span class="p">();</span>

<span class="nv">$inspetor</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">trackEventDeletion</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$event</span><span class="p">);</span>

<span class="cp">?&gt;</span>
</code></pre>
<p>Send information to Inspetor every time an Event listing is deleted from your platform</p>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Argument</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>event</td>
<td>Inspetor/Model/<a href="#inspetorevent">InspetorEvent</a></td>
<td>The Event that is being deleted</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</p>
